## Anti-Patterns
- Multiple tool calls per response.
- Unscoped/unbounded repo scans or log dumps.
- Assuming file existence or project structure.
- Non-idempotent edits or duplicate insertions.
- Continuing after validation failure.
- Ignoring DRY_RUN semantics.

